snippet.title: Nickelodeon Kart Racers 3: Slime Speedway Trailer
snippet.description: The next generation of Nickelodeon Kart Racers is here! Rebuilt and re-imagined from the ground up, Nickelodeon Kart Racers returns - bigger and better than ever! Featuring a cast of 40 iconic characters, drift, slide and boost your way to the finish line on tracks inspired by legendary Nickelodeon shows like SpongeBob SquarePants, Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles, Avatar: The Last Airbender and more!
